name: FruitStand
0:
”Alexa, ask Fruit Stand, how do I store parsley?”
”Alexa, ask Fruit Stand, how do I store these bananas?”
”Alexa, ask Fruit Stand, how do I store cucumbers?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fruit stand
des: This skill helps you find out whether you should put fruits or vegetables in the refrigerator or in the pantry. For example, you can ask Fruit Stand, "How do I store bananas?"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
